---
title: "withdraw (AuctionBidder)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_validate: onlyRole(DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE)
    q_validate --> q_check_to: to == address(0)
    q_check_to --> q_revert: true
    q_check_to --> q_iter: false
    q_revert --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroAddress()
    q_iter --> q_transfer: i < assetAmounts.length
    q_iter --> [*]: i >= assetAmounts.length
    q_transfer --> q_iter: safeTransfer(to, assetAmount.amount); i++

    note right of q_check_to
        INV-001: recipient address must not be zero
    end note

    note right of q_iter
        INV-002: all assets in assetAmounts are transferred to the same recipient
        INV-003: loop iterates exactly assetAmounts.length times
    end note
